{"tid":2461383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港交所前CEO 李小加：每個年輕人都應該參與一次革命","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:41:32.000Z","uid":293677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"009e2bf7ca8d95a509411500b09ede47467b7378","tid":2461383,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"港交所（0388）前行政總裁李小加言論一向「出位」，佢昨日出席瑞信亞洲投資論壇（AIC），講到早排美國散戶齊齊推高美股GameStop（GME），成功「挾爆」沽空機構，佢就自爆兒子當時都有份買入GME，仲話「每個年輕人都應該參與一次革命」，同個仔講呢個就係佢嘅革命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1616507250453&amp;issue=20210323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1616507250453%26issue%3D20210323&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=155cfd8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1616507250453&amp;issue=20210323</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">反了！反了！</span>"},{"pid":"04a1c2d6fafd263f94acaede4b6e94e199a6a0ed","tid":2461383,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"李小加違反《國安法》<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9854b2d0b56f6aed2475c66ea7e6268fb5747f40","tid":2461383,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:41:32.000Z","msg":"煽動分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}